fr:mainmatter.fr:p:
If this condition is satisfied for arbitrary p and q, then by induction on r we have
         F^{p+r} \cap  dF^p         = dF^{p+r}       
which, for large p+r, can be written as
         F^p \cap  dK         = dF^p.       \tag{2}
